column5: 1st nice bass was on a Wave finesse Worm, Crank baits working good plus the last one was on a Buzz bait, we had a pretty good night, these are some of the bass caught Moe was happy 3 of his 4 bass came in about 35 minutes about 6pm his last 1 about 10pm Richard I'm not sure how to make a fancy post but I'll try this
